A new approach for the interpretation of CT models, based on a trend-vector procedure (see Section 5.2.3.3), has been proposed to solve this problem. It allows for the determination of the quantitative influence of descriptors used in the model built on the investigated property [Eq. (5-11)]:(5-11)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
